                    <h2 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1545086839240-nomination-process" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1545086839240-nomination-process" aria-controls="accordion-content-1545086839240-nomination-process" aria-expanded="false">
                            Nomination process
